{"tid":981981,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣工研院 開始 禁 華為 電話電腦","createTime":"2019-01-14T17:21:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-14T18:10:54.000Z","uid":194415,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f53bbe7149a1fcbc1b228f96b27f2beef8d62cc0","tid":981981,"uid":194415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T17:21:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.finance.appledaily.com/realtime/20190114/1500596/?utm_campaign=twad_social_apple.realtimenews&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.finance.appledaily.com%2Frealtime%2F20190114%2F1500596%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dtwad_social_apple.realtimenews%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=Rwj3M8Xzr69VNl9Qpra8CP1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=8fe0e496\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.finance.appledaily.com%2Frealtime%2F20190114%2F1500596%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dtwad_social_apple.realtimenews%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=e3046a71\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.finance.appledaily.com/realtime/20190114/1500596/?utm_campaign=twad_social_apple.realtimenews&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a><br />\n<br />\n敬告全院同仁：<br />\n 「為避免潛在的資安風險，自明（1月15日）日中午起，於本院之辦公場所全面禁止使用華為手機、電腦等。若目前仍有（或準備使用）與實驗有關的華為設備，也請馬上與資科中心聯絡。」<br />\n<br />\n工研院今天晚間6點57分公告如下<br />\n「工研院為國家科技研發單位，許多研發內容涉及機密，為維護資訊安全，遵循政府政策，若是使用華為手機將無法使用工研院的無線內部網路。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n真係好遲鈍<br />\n不過遲禁好過唔禁"},{"pid":"41f9d6da94b72cb63187fb0a1c52164331125d12","tid":981981,"uid":220701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T17:23:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n抵讚"},{"pid":"00c9421d52d4eb30209195472feef